Key Match Events: Ryan Christie scored the opening goal in the 58th minute.
Che Adams scored the second goal in the 85th minute.
Post-Match Reflections: Liam Cooper limped off injured in the second half.
Lyndon Dykes suffered an ankle injury in training.
Stuart Armstrong, Scott McTominay, Ben Doak, and John Souttar are still missing due to injuries.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Gibraltar conceded 41 goals in eight European qualifiers.
Grant Hanley made his first Scotland appearance since March 2023 and his first start in three months.
